=================================
SwiftCode
=================================
SwiftCode is an online platform for testing, developing and participating in technical discussions.
=================================
Pre-Requisites to run the application:
=================================
* Java 1.8 - Download [here](http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html)
* MySQL database server - Download [here](https://dev.mysql.com/downloads/mysql/)
* GCC and G++ packages - Download [here](http://win-builds.org/doku.php/download_and_installation_from_windows)
* Python 2.7 - Download [here](https://www.python.org/downloads/release/python-2713/)
=================================
Running the application:
=================================
The application is packaged with activator command that is used to run with SBT targets
To clean the target folder use:

```
#!shell

activator clean
```

To compile to target, use:

```
#!shell

activator compile
```

To update SBT dependencies, use:

```
#!shell

activator update
```

To run the application in DEV mode, use:

```
#!shell

activator -Dconfig.resource=DEV.conf run
```


To run the application in PROD mode, use:

```
#!shell

swiftcode -Dconfig.resource=PROD.conf -Dhttp.port=80
```